dc_title_s: Outline map of Deal Lake, Monmouth County, N.J. indicating restoration areas & recreational locations made for the Deal Lake Commission
dc_description_s: A map outlining the areas surrounding Deal Lake in Monmouth County, including recreational areas as well as areas in need of restoration.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|This single map was originally part of a set of seven, per the inset label in the upper right corner.
